outh-bow-25-percent-tariff-on-canadian-imports-to-us", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 18:13:47"}, {"id": "4743030", "title": "Carlisle Companies: Trump's Policies, Industry Trends To Aid Earnings", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/858503152/image_858503152.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"3d kehystalo\" data-id=\"858503152\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"960px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/858503152/image_858503152.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/858503152/image_858503152.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/858503152/image_858503152.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/858503152/image_858503152.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/858503152/image_858503152.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/858503152/image_858503152.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/858503152/image_858503152.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/858503152/image_858503152.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Madmaxer/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Founded in 1917, <strong>Carlisle Companies Incorporated </strong>(<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CSL\" title=\"Carlisle Companies Incorporated\">CSL</a></span>) manufactures energy-efficient building solutions such as roofing products, insulation, waterproofing, and engineered HVAC products. The company has two segments, Construction Materials and Weatherproofing Technologies, with 75% and 25% of total revenues, respectively, </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/858503152/image_858503152.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743030-carlisle-companies-trump-policies-industry-trends-to-aid-earnings", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 18:05:47"}, {"id": "4743028", "title": "SNDL Shows Continued Improved Financials And Free Cash Flow For Q3-2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://media.gettyimages.com/id/1419163520/photo/macro-cannabis-flower-on-white-background.jpg?b=1&amp;s=612x612&amp;w=0&amp;k=20&amp;c=JI3HVVs661gHCZZ3cgYa-yDGARpoqz_B1GCmD9Kq6AU=\" alt=\"Macro Cannabis Flower on White Background\" data-id=\"1419163520\" data-type=\"getty-image\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">carlofranco/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>SNDL (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SNDL\" title=\"SNDL Inc.\">SNDL</a></span>) reported Q3-2024 financials last month (11/05) and showed marked improvement in performance. The stock price is down 8% since I <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4713628-sndl-improved-q2-2024-financials-amidst-sector-uncertainty-hold\">covered</a> the company last August. Over the last twelve months the stock</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743028-sndl-shows-continued-improved-financials-and-free-cash-flow-for-q3-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 18:01:13"}, {"id": "4743025", "title": "BNY Mellon New York AMT-Free Municipal Bond Fund, Inc. Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-